
PACKAGING
=========

from cvs
--------

create a tarball

	cvs checkout gromos++
	cd gromos++
	./Config.sh
	mkdir BUILD
	cd BUILD
	../configure
	make dist

from tarball
------------

take care to use a clean environment
	bash -h
	export PATH=/usr/bin:/bin

	tar zxvf gromos-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
	cd gromos-X.Y.Z
	./configure --prefix=/usr/local/gromos/gromos++
	make
	
	make DESTDIR=/scratch/igcpc01/markus/tmp/package/gromos++ install

	

DEBIAN
------

	check libraries
	ldd tser
	apt-cache search pattern
	dpkg -S filename

	in the DESTDIR create a DEBIAN directory
	copy the control.debian file to DESTDIR/DEBIAN/control
	
	dpkg --build gromos++

